```

* **Fluxo Earn "Corrida"**: Strava â†’ Webhook â†’ Worker â†’ Redis â†’ Postgres â†’ UX Dashboard.
* **Fluxo Earn "Social"**: OAuth IG/TikTok â†’ Listener â†’ Worker valida â†’ Redis â†’ Postgres.
* **Fluxo Burn**: UI "Resgate" â†’ API â†’ Worker on-chain (mint/burn) â†’ Evento â†’ Dashboard.

